It would be very useful if the complete series of parameters was available as a single variable in User Macros.  It would allow an easy method to pass the parameters straight through to the underlying macros.  In our case, we encapsulate several standard macros, like rate, toc, and info, into a single unit that provides a header on most pages.  We wanted to allow the users to access the parameters on the toc macro without having to process and pass thru each parameter manually.

This functionality would also make it possible to have several variants of the base macro call the original macro and add one or two extra parameters in the process.  This is better than duplicating the logic from the first in all of the variants and having to make sure they are consistent in the future.

